{% set pagename = "Home" %}
{% set pageRef = "" %}
{% set all_projects = projects %}

{% extends "layout.nunjucks" %}

{% block content %}
	<div class="hero__container" container="hero">
   
   <div class="section__container section__container--alt">
      <div class="section__content">
        <div class="flex-content flex-content--alt">
          <div class="flex-content--6">
            <p>
              I am a detail-oriented programmer seeking a collaborative development role between designers and other programmers to contribute multiple years of experience in front-end web development. 
            </p>
            <p>
              Additionally, my passion for project management, emerging technologies and development strategies help push the boundaries of recent experiences. I am always up for the next challenge.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-content--4 center">
            <img class="hero__portrait" src="app/img/profile-image.jpg">
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
  <div class="content">
    <div class="section__container">
      <div class="section__content">
      	<h2 class="section__title" id="section-projects">Projects</h2>
        <hr class="section__rule--projects">
      	<p>
      		Professional work includes a number of small client web projects using custom frameworks built using NPM and Gulp workflows. Larger projects include the development of an internal pattern library to redesign the theme for an umbrella eCommerce site in addition to a modular help system for sales force inquires.
      	</p>

        <p>
          Below are a series of personal projects, using psuedo-tutorials to break down a number of systems used throughout my professional experience.
        </p>

        {% for project in all_projects %}

        <hr class="section__rule--projects-sub">

        <div class="flex-content flex-content--alt">
          <div class="flex-content--4 center">
            <a href="/projects/{{ project.title | replace(' ', '-') | lower }}.html">
              <img class="project__image" src="app/img/{{ project.image }}">
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-content--6">
            <h4 class="marg-top-0">{{ project.title }}</h4>
            {{ project.intro | safe }}
            <a class="button" href="/projects/{{ project.title | replace(' ', '-') | lower }}.html">Read More</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        {% endfor %}

      </div>        
    </div>

    <div class="section__container">
      <div class="section__content">
      	<h2 class="section__title" id="section-resume">Résumé</h2>
        <hr class="section__rule--resume">

        <div class="flex-content">
          <div class="flex-content--5">

            <h3>PROFESSIONAL EXPERIENCE</h3>

            <h4>ALDEN IMAGE -- Shelton, CT</h4>
            <p><b>Interactive Developer</b>, 2015 to 2017</p>
            <p>Hired as a full-time programmer after an enriching internship and subsequent freelance role.</p>

            <ul>
              <li>Improved development workflows using custom frameworks built with NPM and Gulp.</li>
              <li>Developed a pattern library using Nunjucks, SCSS, JSON, JavaScript, and Angular to retheme an eCommerce site that increased redesign efficiency.</li>
              <li>Maintained awareness of web traffic with frequent analytics reports using Google Analytics, Tag Manager, and Data Studio.</li>
              <li>Updated network security and provided recommendations for systems and machines.</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>EXPLETIVE STUDIOS -- Shelton, CT</h4>
            <p><b>Systems Engineer</b>, 2015 to Present</p>
            <p>Led development of a third person, multiplayer game using Unreal Engine 4 and Steamworks.</p>

            <ul>
              <li>Organized task distribution in Asana to coordinate development between rapid prototype builds.</li>
              <li>Developed an asset selection and instantiation system using C++ with network replication.</li>
            </ul>

          </div>
          <div class="flex-content--5">

            <h3>SKILLS</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Rapid Prototyping</li>
              <li>Documenting</li>
              <li>Unit Testing</li>
              <li>Debugging</li>
              <li>Refactoring</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>TECHNOLOGY OVERVIEW</h3>
            <p>Languages: C++, JavaScript, TypeScript, CSS, SCSS, HTML, Nunjucks, JSON, XML, PHP</p>
            <p>Workflows: Gulp</p>
            <p>Frameworks: Angular</p>
            <p>Services: Git, Asana, JIRA, Wordpress, Adobe CC</p>

            <h3>EDUCATION</h3>
            <p>WESTERN CONNECTICUT STATE UNIVERSITY -- Danbury, CT</p>
            <p><b>Bachelor of Science in Computer Science</b>, Minor in Business Management</p>

          </div>
          <div class="flex-content--10">

            <a class="button" href="app/pdfs/PatrickPetrushonis-Resume.pdf" target="_blank">View PDF Version</a>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
{% endblock %}